{"tid":737952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佳寶集團3肉檔遭連環淋漂白水 至少3職員受傷送院","createTime":"2018-07-11T07:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T08:24:46.000Z","uid":184261,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"731ce557c3402ca3f8e0ff0fdeacc5170de1fb3e","tid":737952,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"佳寶集團在慈雲山毓華里、蒲崗村道及美孚三間肉檔，今午先後遭人連環淋漂白水施襲。其中在慈雲山毓華里華基大樓地下佳寶屬下的一間肉檔，下午1時20分，一人掩至向職員淋疑似漂白水的液體，至少兩名職員受傷要送院。<br />\n<br />\n幾乎同一時間，相隔100米左右、蒲崗村道99號佳寶特賣場內的豬肉檔同樣被人淋懷疑漂白水，無人受傷。另外在美孚的肉檔亦有一名職員被淋傷。<br />\n<br />\n警方在蒲崗村道89號外一個垃圾桶內，發現兩隻紙杯及一頂鴨舌帽，正封鎖各現場調查，以及追追緝施襲者歸案。<br />\n<br />\n毓華里現場附近一間店舖的女職員說：「見到佢丟咗隻杯響度，跟住走去後面，走咗。」她指該名可疑人戴帽、穿花衫，撞開其他人逃去，兩名豬肉檔職員受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180711/58428710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180711%2F58428710&d=ePjZ8s8nzOd0IjjNpBSjjzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=79184c80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180711%2F58428710&h=3abd9aaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180711/58428710</a><br />\n<br />\n佳寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15db358fd53c77a747d822b5b240a69a25d03cd5","tid":737952,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:32:31.000Z","msg":"漂白水要幾高濃度先受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪恐嚇佢地先, 下次先用漒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98566904390853746a985fa5c8adab5f2118ebb2","tid":737952,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:32:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd168e4e5b0f05b44c17bdd6b4d63c8a1709c69b","tid":737952,"uid":16676,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"用漂水, 只係唔想佢做生意<br />\n淋落d 豬肉度<br />\n<br />\n不過佳寶都怪怪地, 係個商場向當眼通道開肉檔<br />\n<br />\n攪到成個場成陣味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好黑人憎<br />\n<br />\n你係超市裡面就話遮, 賣埋d 大陸死豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdd0d2048449382d34de01dd52c9701df982ec9","tid":737952,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:50:22.000Z","msg":"呢間野超污穢，執左佢啦"},{"pid":"f4239453b866994fd8e7e2226283d06a865e1390","tid":737952,"uid":88841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"試過買包廚師腸返黎解完凍，成個包裝入面d腸流晒d黑色血水出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c658771f800cf6144e103db22abf42fe19c1b3","tid":737952,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"照賣 !"},{"pid":"6dce818b80f7806d9aef01a5d97653b102a165fa","tid":737952,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}